16:41.326 --> 16:50.175
telescope, and they'd just go haywire. And you 
realized all over again what got you into

16:50.696 --> 16:55.641
astronomy in the first place. You start telling 
them how the light's been coming since before the

16:55.861 --> 17:01.947
pyramids were built and so on. The mystery and 
wonder of it, the public brings that back. And

17:07.773 --> 17:09.375
that's a great thing. I was just always well 
