17:46.884 --> 17:57.239
down the law, laid down the law that he was the one 
that was supposed to be the communication with the

17:46.884 --> 17:57.239
town. And other astronomers were not supposed to 
talk about what was going on at Lowell. And it's

18:02.186 --> 18:06.852
just such a defeating, self-defeating Well, 
